<s1 id=CalendarMonthWindow>Calendar Month View
<!--	<idx>Calendar view, month view window<sort>calendar view, month view window<\idx> -->
	<idx>month view window, Calendar view<sort>month view window, calendar view<\idx>

<newline>&empty;

Month view displays the appointments in a calendar month.  
You can change the display 
using the Previous view (left) and Next view (right) navigation arrows
or by clicking the Day, Week, or Year view icon.

<newline>&empty;

<figure nonumber entity=Calendar-Month-View>
<\figure>

<procedure>See Also
<list bullet tight>
<item> <xref CalendarWeekWindow>
<item> <xref CalendarDayWindow>
<item> <xref CalendarYearWindow>
<\list>

<s1 id=CalendarWeekWindow>Calendar Week View
<!--	<idx>Calendar view, week view window<sort>calendar view, week view window<\idx> -->
	<idx>week view window, Calendar view<sort>week view window, calendar view<\idx>
	<idx>grid, week view<\idx>
	<idx>week view, grid<\idx>

<newline>&empty;

Week view displays the appointments in a calendar week (Mon-Sun).  
You can change the display 
using the Previous view (left) and Next view (right) navigation arrows
or by clicking the Day, Month, or Year view icon.

Week view includes a grid for the entire week showing shaded areas where 
appointments are scheduled.

<newline>&empty;

<figure nonumber entity=Calendar-Week-View>
<\figure>

<procedure>See Also
<list bullet tight>
<item> <xref CalendarMonthWindow>
<item> <xref CalendarDayWindow>
<item> <xref CalendarYearWindow>
<\list>

<s1 id=CalendarDayWindow>Calendar Day View
<!--	<idx>Calendar view, day view window<sort>calendar view, day view window<\idx> -->
	<idx>day view window, Calendar view<sort>day view window, calendar view<\idx>
	<idx>three-month mini-calendar, day view<\idx>
	<idx>day view, three-month mini-calendar<\idx>

<newline>&empty;

Day view displays the appointments in a calendar day.  
You can change the display 
using the Previous view (left) and Next view (right) navigation arrows
or by clicking the Week, Month, or Year view icon.

Day view includes a three-month mini-calendar containing day and month 
buttons for navigation.  Click on the month buttons to change the calendar
to Month view; click on the day buttons to change the calendar to Day view.

<newline>&empty;

<figure nonumber entity=Calendar-Day-View>
<\figure>

