<!--	<idx>Calendar view, year view window<sort>calendar view, year view window<\idx> -->
	<idx>year view window, Calendar view<sort>year view window, calendar view<\idx>

<newline>&empty;

Year view displays a calendar year.  You can change the display 
with the Previous view (left) and Next view (right) navigation arrows
or by clicking the Day, Week, or Month view icon.

<newline>&empty;

<figure nonumber entity=Calendar-Year-View>
