<s1 id=CalendarOptionsCategoryDialog>Calendar Options Dialog Box
	<idx>Options dialog box, reference<sort>options dialog box, reference<\idx>
<!--	<idx>Options dialog box, Category menu<sort>options dialog box, category menu<\idx> -->
	<idx>Category menu, in Options dialog box<sort>category menu, in options dialog box<\idx>
<!--	<idx>Options dialog box, OK button<sort>options dialog box, ok button<\idx> -->
	<idx>OK button, in Options dialog box<sort>ok button, in options dialog box<\idx>
<!--	<idx>Options dialog box, Apply button<sort>options dialog box, apply button<\idx> -->
	<idx>Apply button, in Options dialog box<sort>apply button, in options dialog box<\idx>
<!--	<idx>Options dialog box, Reset button<sort>options dialog box, reset button<\idx> -->
	<idx>Reset button, in Options dialog box<sort>reset button, in options dialog box<\idx>
<!--	<idx>Options dialog box, Cancel button<sort>options dialog box, cancel button<\idx> -->
	<idx>Cancel button, in Options dialog box<sort>cancel button, in options dialog box<\idx>
<!--	<idx>Options dialog box, Help button<sort>options dialog box, help button<\idx> -->
	<idx>Help button, in Options dialog box<sort>help button, in options dialog box<\idx>

<newline>&empty;

<p>To change the default settings for all new appointments and to 
customize your Calendar display, choose Options from the File menu.  
Additional customizable options are available on the Category menu:

<list bullet tight>
<item> <link hyperlink=CalendarOptionsEditorDialog>Editor Defaults<\link>
<item> <link hyperlink=CalendarOptionsDisplayDialog>Display Settings<\link>
<item> <link hyperlink=CalendarOptionsAccessDialog>Access List and Permissions<\link>
<item> <link hyperlink=CalendarOptionsPrinterDialog>Printer Settings<\link>
<item> <link hyperlink=CalendarOptionsDateDialog>Date Format<\link>
<\list>

<note>You can override the defaults for individual appointments using the 
<link hyperlink=CalendarApptEditorDialog>Appointment Editor<\link>.
<\note>

<newline>&empty;
<p>The following controls are common to all the Options categories:

<figure nonumber entity=Calendar-Options>
<\figure>

<lablist nowrap>
\ Category \	A menu of dialog boxes you can use to customize Calendar.

\ OK \		Applies changes and closes the dialog box.
\ Apply \	Changes the options you've edited.
\ Reset \	Resets options to the way they were since you last applied them.
\ Cancel \	Closes the dialog box without applying your changes.
\ Help \	Displays help for this dialog box.
<\lablist>

