	<idx>Default View, in Display Settings dialog box<sort>default view, in display settings dialog box<\idx>
	<idx>Initial Calendar View, in Display Settings dialog box<sort>initial calendar view, in display settings dialog box<\idx>
	<idx> Federated Naming Service<sort>federated naming service<\idx> 
	<idx> calendar naming, federated naming service<\idx> 
