selected in the Browse Menu list.<newline>
<term nogloss>Schedule<\term> opens the Group Appointment Editor.<newline>
<term nogloss>Mail<\term> starts Mailer, a mail application.<newline>
<term nogloss>Cancel<\term> closes the Compare Calendars dialog box.<newline>
<term nogloss>Help<\term> displays help for this dialog box.

